---
title: Tex-Mex Veggie Mince Tacos with Caramelised Onion & Plant-Based Aioli
description: Savoury veggie mince and sweet caramelised onions are the stars of this crowd-pleasing meal. Easy and satisfying, the tacos
come together in a snap, with lots of plant-based additions for everyone to build their own and join in the fun!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-veggie-mince-tacos-bf2f89ed.jpg
